{"tid":2310071,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"廚絲食記@米豬連泰國菜","createTime":"2020-12-03T04:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T09:25:41.000Z","uid":205222,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c5cf756f0bf5bc0bef2249b1066041e65699c9f","tid":2310071,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T04:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無得去旅行，睇住之前去旅行既相止住渴先<br />\n上年去曼谷既時候，搵咗間米芝蓮餐廳食fusion 菜既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲相係濛既，因為我求其搵電話影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個環境好relax 好chill,店主仲自己種左一大片rosemary 園，好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OyTPaBG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyTPaBG.png&h=a8b5bac1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KqaYOou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKqaYOou.png&h=f91f9bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8tvEAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8tvEAz.png&h=726cdcac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzyjxVK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzyjxVK.png&h=08160fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AhtjxVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAhtjxVS.png&h=0a2ddef0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iN8Ltuj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiN8Ltuj.png&h=8709856d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z237GPt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz237GPt.png&h=3396f5d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HOJWz9D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHOJWz9D.png&h=85c12966&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W5Y7GPO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW5Y7GPO.png&h=2eb9304b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個甜品係jasmine rice ice cream,<br />\n係目前為止食過最好食嘅雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好掛住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38b6305fc756fa0b2d1abcc6edf1c8aa126d892","tid":2310071,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"請換左電話再影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6399b4fab2c96c6b3bacedc2190313ef28bb8f4","tid":2310071,"uid":116087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:21:41.000Z","msg":"間野咩名?"},{"pid":"b4ee7a1981e6182006f379448c025d548901c1a0","tid":2310071,"uid":205222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38b6305fc756fa0b2d1abcc6edf1c8aa126d892","tid":2310071,"uid":194483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:13:47.000Z","msg":"請換左電話再影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T08:26:36.000Z","msg":"窮撚要用電話用到最後一刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7703ba47ac9a751ee877bc00349eb6a668a55d86","tid":2310071,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"影到成pat屎咁點撚樣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}